  <body>

  <p>
A 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_sustainability_and_transformation_partnership">Sustainability and Transformation Partnership</xref>
 (
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_sustainability_and_transformation_partnership">STP</xref>
) is an integral part of 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_nhs_england">NHS England</xref>
.  </p>
  <p>
A 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_sustainability_and_transformation_partnership">Sustainability and Transformation Partnership</xref>
 is where local NHS 
    <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_organisation">ORGANISATIONS</xref>
 and 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_local_authority">Local Authorities</xref>
 draw up shared proposals to improve health and care in the areas they serve.  </p>
  <p>
In some areas 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_sustainability_and_transformation_partnership">Sustainability and Transformation Partnerships</xref>
 have evolved to become 
    <xref href="http://www.datadictionary.nhs.uk/web_site_content/supporting_definitions/integrated_care_system.asp"
            scope="external"
            format="html">Integrated Care Systems</xref>
, a new form of even closer collaboration between the NHS and 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_local_authority">Local Authorities</xref>
.  </p>
  <p>
For further information on 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_sustainability_and_transformation_partnership">Sustainability and Transformation Partnerships</xref>
, see the 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_nhs_england">NHS England</xref>
 website at: 
    <xref href="https://www.england.nhs.uk/integratedcare/stps/"
            scope="external"
            format="html">Sustainability and transformation partnerships</xref>
.  </p>

